      • generateID

        public static AgentID generateID(java.lang.String basename)
        factory function
        Parameters:
        basename - the basename for the agent ID
        Returns:
        a new unique AgentID based on the basename plus a unique serial number. These are unique only for a single run of the system, you can not assume new generated IDs to be different from IDs generated in earlier runs.
